_sText: Counter-Terrorists : Our team of the most elite must prevent the Terrorists from bombing any of the chemical weapon crates. Squad members must defuse any bombs that threaten targeted areas or neutralize all terrorists before they have a chance of carrying out their threats. All Terrorists must be considered extremely dangerous. Terrorists : Your squad of independence fighters has been tasked with releasing Sentox Nerv Gas inside The Marr Freight Company. The damage to the surrounding city will force the Americans to take into our demands. The Terrorist carrying the C4 must destroy one of the chemical weapon stashes we plant! Our Targeted areas are the main level garage and underground generator room.
